            <title>[LU-12929] Field net_state in struct lnet_net is never used, only set.  It should be discarded</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12929</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lnet_net.net_state is set, but never used.&lt;/p&gt;

